sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as User (Browser)
    participant ClerkFE as Clerk Provider<br/>(Frontend)
    participant ClerkCloud as Clerk Cloud
    participant API as ASP.NET Core API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,DB: — Sign-Up / First Sign-In —

    User->>ClerkFE: Click Sign In / Sign Up
    ClerkFE->>ClerkCloud: Redirect to Clerk Hosted UI
    User->>ClerkCloud: Enter credentials / OAuth
    ClerkCloud-->>ClerkFE: JWT (id_token + access_token)
    ClerkFE->>ClerkFE: Store session (cookies)

    Note over User,DB: — Authenticated API Request —

    User->>ClerkFE: Navigate to protected page
    ClerkFE->>API: GET /api/jobs/employer<br/>Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
    API->>API: JwtBearerHandler validates JWT<br/>against Clerk authority
    API->>API: OnTokenValidated callback

    alt New user (sub not in DB)
        API->>DB: INSERT INTO AspNetUsers<br/>(FirstName, LastName, Email)
        API->>DB: INSERT INTO UserRoles<br/>(UserId, RoleId = Applicant)
    end

    API->>DB: Query user + roles
    DB-->>API: ApplicationUser + Claims
    API->>API: Map claims to HttpContext.User<br/>(NameIdentifier, Email, Role)

    alt [Authorize(Roles = "Employer,Admin")]
        API->>API: Check role claim
        alt User has required role
            API-->>User: 200 OK — Resource data
        else Missing role
            API-->>User: 403 Forbidden — Insufficient permissions
        end
    else AllowAnonymous
        API-->>User: 200 OK — Public data
    end

    API-->>ClerkFE: JSON Response
    ClerkFE-->>User: Render UI
